Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz32.82\move(1383,152,1374,953)}拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz22.07\move(483,194,501,962)}双重反击!!
