Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要画设计图呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我们在设计什么东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要拼起来就可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们打钉子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边这么顺利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 这种时候不冷静的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想不到好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主意 主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱家里 厕所门上不是有个把手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怎么看都像只鸭子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 小夏想到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越用力想 越是什么都想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么新奇的主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非小夏 真的觉得我什么都没想到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我一直在装没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是开个玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢思考这种尖端科技了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是折刀的刀柄部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 自信爆表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 如果你叫我『会走路的活字典』我会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活字典本来就会走路的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我来划线做标记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏用锯子沿线锯木板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锯完之后要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按我说的顺序钉上钉子固定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先用那块板作为底座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那块大板立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右边一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是莲酱想出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都觉得做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 这是用来干什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我现在就用一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要睡觉啊 还管不管！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 最后做成这样了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 书架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是咖喱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我要开始上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校的咖喱和莲华…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个组合…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过莲华应该不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做梦也想不到本校会发生那种大悲剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下课啦 下课啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去玩积木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把娃娃带到学校呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生没问题呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课的时候是收起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老师看到的话要没收的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师说过上课的时候不要玩就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 今天日影休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明昨天还是活蹦乱跳的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 今天的午饭是咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影那份也可以吃掉了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 好歹稍微关心下日影呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那木实就只有一份咖喱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行 我也很想多吃咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曹操到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得好晚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了点麻烦事所以迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 迟到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不~行呀 不~行呀 我~要告诉老~师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐背着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影 学校不准带那种东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老师看到的话要没收的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 在动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把我家妹妹当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母发烧去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在学校照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才迟到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话请假不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的午餐是咖喱 所以不能请假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 竟然记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么卖零食的 给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师说了 年纪最大的卖零食的要负责照顾莲华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 这种事情木实更适合做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说 决定好的事情也不会改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了哦大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂木实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 小夏和小鞠一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛君也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要逃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我抱也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会哄小孩子 真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华见到有兴趣的东西就会咬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好吗 她很喜欢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿嗒嗒的 我要去洗一下校服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华的奶嘴掉地上了 我也要去洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要创造积木高度的新纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那两个人把小孩丢下跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 这孩子已经会走路了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的过来了呀 好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海的最高纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高纪录…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高纪录…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只剩下一块了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 一点小事哭什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家之后我把零食分你一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害呢 小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经三年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小事当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生小吉先生 小吉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生湿嗒嗒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华她… 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非去走廊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊里没看见呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进配膳室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叫人操心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是主菜桶 你准备对咖喱做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华把咖喱当成人质… 咖喱质了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华 Stop Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱咖喱咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待很久的咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱咖喱咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 莲酱第一次上学就把学校镇压下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法忘记那个瞬间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲戚送的梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞌睡防止装置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是莲华做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要怎么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扫卫生差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书得放好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 踩到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什么呀 弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比以前更破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破成这样不能要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮忙找下我的弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到的话会很痛 所以要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那表情怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和体检完之后的表情一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我踩到你的弹力球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便跑进我的房间玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在那里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是宝物的话为什么会丢在我的房间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是丢在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是刚好找到以前喜欢的弹力球 丢着玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不还是在丢么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 接下来要做什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要把书收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相册？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很老的照片了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么我脸上有伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得是小吉先生掉到门外 去捡的时候摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 没预先联系就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 外面很热呢 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤好像做了不少我的布娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上什么都没有却摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对… 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自做的那些布娃娃果然还是很糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不糟糕呀 做得很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候喜欢的娃娃变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你教我怎么样把它补好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁 裁缝工具在我的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以进萤的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也带了裁缝工具过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了这么多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤真的很喜欢娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这方面很像个小学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呀 也不要只做我的娃娃 做点其他人的娃娃怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都做一样的很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不会无聊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样才能补好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经破得很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得用新布重新做一个可能会更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就会变成另一个娃娃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要打补丁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那里应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤做得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了 萤下次来我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 吃晚饭了 来拿餐具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 那个弹力球怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放回壁橱的玩具箱里面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心不要再丢掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然后悔也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然学起大人说话来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大人了呀
